  %h2.hat Why this website?
  %p I build this website because there is no <strong>simple</strong> way for people to play with soft focus effet. I want to allow everybody to use it <strong>wihtout</strong> any photo editing skills. It's a <strong>fun</strong> effect a lot a people ignore which make your photos look more <strong>dreamy</strong>.
